project: Foul demons have infested this forest. You must free it!
Boars are hardy and stay on the ground.
Stags have less health, but can jump.
Press or hold Z to fire your bow.
Press X to dash and evade damage.
This takes you to the next level and restores your health.
The Horned Demon Cernun was Defeated! The forest is free, for now...
Kuricommander(me!) for sprites and programming. Viscount of Birds for Level design.
